For HiveServer2 embedded mode (jdbc:hive2://) I am going to remove the default initialization to use mr engine as it causes the program termination for some reason:

{code}
<name>hplsql.conn.init.hiveconn</name>
  <value>
     set hive.execution.engine=mr; 
     use default;
  </value>
{code}
